Subject: Upload of old rules and old action plan to a new server
Description:
We setup a new PingCasltle Server and now is the question how to import the old Action Plans and the Rules.
I found the export button but no way to put all the Rules back in with an upload. 
Is there an easy way to upload the csv file?
Solution_Comment__c:
Hello Benjamin,

The feature is currently missing and needs to be added to the roadmap.

If you have access to both new and old database this can be done manually but you'd need to plan a call with Mr. Vincent Le TOux, the developer of this product.
The idea is to generate a sql script that will apply the changes to the database.
